categories: Category:Military officers of the Sith Empire

nodes.text: An Imperial lieutenant commanded a squad of Imperial soldiers during the Galactic War on Hoth. He guided an Imperial boarding party tasked with attacked a crashed dreadnaught, home of the White Maw, in an attempt to eliminate the pirate captain Valon, but met the Barsen'thor. The lieutenant's unit had been tasked with killing Valon in return for the pirate betraying the Empire after they gave him the regenerative armor.
